snippet.textDisplay: To those who think that LEBRON ought to stay away from CHEERING his son in BB activities/events, there is something inherently WRONG with that kind of thinking! It is quite the contrary! Parents, from a nurturing and psychological frame, MUST show up to solidify LOVE for their offspring.  That is the very premise that makes me love and cherish the Mr. L James and his wife.  Already, I can discern a GOOD pattern of behavior from BRONNY who is emulating LEBRON's BB intelligence and prowess.  To the JAMES' family...in particular to the young son, TEN THOUSAND CONGRATULATIONS! Being born with an innate ability to do something is quite a blessing; having parents to help propel a child unto that ability and sustain it is another abstract of WONDER! I hope I get to see LEBRON one day.  Buona fortuna a BRONNY! Il mio amore fraterno e forte … alla famiglia James!
